\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 206\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -207\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 Notizen zur Kontroverse zwischen {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes Gerson}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  und {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Jan van Schoonhoven}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  \u252 \'fcber {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Jan van Ruusbroecs}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  ,{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De ornatu spiritualis desponsationis\rquote }}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , Pars III, mit Exzerpt aus {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes Gerson}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 : {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Epistola II ad fratrem Bartholomaeum}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  sowie Exzerpten aus Werken des Jan van Ruusbroec\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Doctor Johannes Gerson scripsit contra hanc terciam partem domini Ruysbroeck unam epistolam in qua repudiat omnia que in ista iam dicta tercia parte scripta sunt. Econtra frater Johannes de Scoenhauia canonicus regularis in Viridi valle \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [Groenendaal] \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 scripsit unam epistulam contra Gersonem in qua defendit suprascriptam terciam partem ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [unterer Teil von 206\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  mit Papier (6 x 14,5 cm) \u252 \'fcberklebt, darauf vom Schreiber:] \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Econtra Gerson scripsit unam epistolam ad unum de patribus maioris Carthusie nomine Bartholomeus. In qua epistola idem Gerson scribit contra defensionem Johannis de Schoenhauia ymmo contra istam excelentissimam contemplacionem etc. Tamen in eadem epistola eciam aliqua consona et consolatoria ymmo et sana inseruit verba ita scribens ait: Vide inquit queso o lector si modestior esse potuerit sermo meus ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (207\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... Item in uno loco unius de libris suis cuius principium non vidi scribit de quadruplici felicitate. Et ibidem de quarta felicitate sic ait: Super has est quarta felicitas ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  ... non ita prebuisset occasionem errandi et se culpandi. 
